/ Header
%header
  .container
    .intro-text
      / .intro-lead-in We Build Practical And Elegant Solutions
      .intro-heading  We Build Practical And Elegant Solutions
      %a.page-scroll.btn.btn-xl{:href => "#services"} Tell Me More
/ Services Section
%section#services
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-12.text-center
        %h2.section-heading Services
        %h3.section-subheading.text-muted Reliable, Practical, and Comprehensive
    .row.text-center
      .col-md-4
        %span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
          %i.fa.fa-tablet.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        %h4.service-heading Mobile
        %p.text-muted We focus on Android, whether it's building your cool idea or rescuing an app from failling. We have iOS friends and can connect you.
      .col-md-4
        %span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
          %i.fa.fa-laptop.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        %h4.service-heading Web
        %p.text-muted We love building with Ruby on Rails, Node, and .Net. API - check. Desktop and mobile - check.
        %a.page-scroll{:href => "#contact"} Check with us
        to find out more.
      .col-md-4
        %span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
          %i.fa.fa-database.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        %h4.service-heading Data
        %p.text-muted Sql or NoSql with a dash of big data (ElasticSearch). We know when to use which, and how to make them sing.
