/ About Section
%section#about
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-12.text-center
        %h2.section-heading About
        %h3.section-subheading.text-muted We solve problems with software and sometimes hardware.
    .row
      .col-lg-12.text-center.text-muted
        %h4.section-subheading.text-muted We Build What Works
        %p The goal was always to build the best pragmatic solutions for our customers, regardless of technologies. The result has been mixes of .Net, Android, Ruby on Rails, and Node; with databases ranging from SQL Server to PostgresSQL to MongoDB. Even an ElasticSearch appearance. We design and build what you need AND what fits for your needs.
    .row
      .col-lg-12.text-center.text-muted
        %h4.section-subheading.text-muted What We Build With
        %p We have expertise in: .Net, Ruby on Rails, Node, Javascript, Android, SQL (most variants), MongoDB, and all things web. We love the modern frameworks and tools like jQuery, React, Angular, Less, and Bootstrap.

